) Name: Mr. Santosh Marutirao Kamble Designation: Public Information Officer Address: COCSIT Campus, Ambajogai Road, Latur Phone: 9420213625 Email: santosh.kamble@cocsit.org.in How to File an RTI Application Submit a written application in English, Hindi, or the official language of the area. Clearly specify the information required. Pay the prescribed application fee (usually ₹10). Send the application to the PIO via post or submit it in person. Fee Details Application Fee: ₹10 Additional charges may apply for copies/documents as per RTI rules. Time Limit 30 days from the date of receipt of the application. 48 hours in case of information concerning life and liberty. Proactive Disclosures In accordance with Section 4(1)(b) of the RTI Act, the following information is available on the website: Organizational structure Functions and duties Powers and duties of officers Rules, regulations, and manuals Directory of employees Budget and expenditure Details of facilities available to students Download RTI Documents RTI Act, 2005 RTI Rules Application Form (PDF) Note: Information that falls under exemptions specified in the RTI Act (Section 8 & 9) may not be disclosed. Syllabus Open Syllabus of All Courses! REV. CBCS UG COURSES (Revised CBCS) UG FY 2019-20 B.Sc (CS) - FY B.Sc (SE) - FY B.Sc (NT) - FY B.Sc (BT) - FY BCA - FY UG SY 2020-21 BCA SY B.Sc (CS) - SY B.Sc (SE) - SY B.Sc (NT) - SY UG TY 2021-22 BCA TY B.Sc. (CS) - TY B.Sc. (SE) - TY B.Sc. (NT) - TY B.Voc(SD) - FY SY TY BBA - TY B.Sc.Biotechnology - TY UG TY 2025-26 BCA TY B.Sc. (CS) - TY B.Sc. (SE) - TY B.Sc. (NT) - TY B.Sc. (CM) - TY B.Sc. (IT) - TY Note: Updated Revised CBCS Syllabus (TY) Uploaded on 13.09.2025 --> TY 2023-24 B.Sc.IT - FY SY TY B.Sc.CM - FY SY TY PG COURSES (Revised CBCS) PG FY Syllabus 2019-20 M.Sc (CS) - FY M.Sc (SE) - FY M.Sc (CM) - FY M.Sc (SAN)- FY M.Sc (BT) - FY PG SY Syllabus 2020-21 M.Sc (CS)- SY M.Sc (SE)- SY M.Sc (CM)- SY M.Sc (SAN)- SY MCA MCA PG FY & SY MCA w.e.f. 2024-25 MCA FY - SE